<BaseLayout
  title="Drive-Thru Near Brentwood, TN | Fresh Coffee & Quick Food to Go"
  description="The Local Drive-Thru in Centerville is just 40 minutes from Brentwood. Fresh espresso, breakfast sandwiches, pastries, and lunch without leaving your car. Perfect for Brentwood commuters."
