      <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-drivethru-centerville" class="hero-cta">Order Ahead</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><span>Drive-Thru Near Brentwood</span></li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <section class="location-intro">
      <h2>The Local Drive-Thru for Brentwood Commuters</h2>
      <p>
        You're leaving Brentwood, heading south on I-65. You want real coffee, not chain coffee. You want a fresh pastry, not something sitting under a heat lamp. You're busy. You don't want to get out of your car. We're 40 minutes south. Order on Clover before you leave, and your latte's ready when you arrive. Real espresso. Fresh pastries. No compromises.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Easy Drive from Brentwood</h3>
        <p><strong>Distance:</strong> 40 minutes south from Brentwood</p>
        <p><strong>Route:</strong> I-65 South → Dickson Exit → TN-100 → Centerville</p>
        <p><strong>On the Way:</strong> If you're heading south anyway, we're basically your pit stop</p>
        <p>
          Comfortable drive. Order ahead on Clover while you're in Brentwood and we'll have your coffee pulled and ready when you pull up to our window.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Why Brentwood Professionals Choose Us</h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li>40 minutes is doable for quality coffee and breakfast.</li>
          <li>Order on Clover. Pick up in 5 minutes. No waiting.</li>
          <li>Real espresso pulled fresh. Not gas station coffee.</li>
          <li>Fresh pastries and breakfast sandwiches daily.</li>
          <li>Quick lunch options when you're on the go.</li>
          <li>Open 5am weekdays for early commuters from Brentwood.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Popular Orders from Brentwood</h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li><strong>Morning Commute:</strong> Cappuccino + fresh croissant</li>
          <li><strong>Pre-Meeting:</strong> Espresso shot + cinnamon roll</li>
          <li><strong>Lunch Break:</strong> Panini or wrap + cold brew</li>
          <li><strong>Afternoon Pick-Me-Up:</strong> Latte + muffin</li>
