        <h3>Hours & Location</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Monday-Friday:</strong> 5 AM - 6 PM<br />
          <strong>Saturday:</strong> 7 AM - 6 PM<br />
          <strong>Sunday:</strong> Closed
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Address:</strong> 1171 TN-100<br />
          Centerville, TN 37033<br />
          <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:(931)729-4821">(931) 729-4821</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>What Brentwood Drivers Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-cards">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>\"I drive from Brentwood down I-65 twice a month. The drive-thru is my new pit stop. Order on my phone before I leave Brentwood, grab real espresso and pastries 40 minutes later. Way better than gas station coffee.\"</p>
          <p><strong>- Karen (Brentwood to Columbia)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>\"Brentwood resident here. My morning commute goes south. Stop by the drive-thru, order ahead, grab fresh coffee. Starts my day right instead of with burnt gas station coffee.\"</p>
          <p><strong>- Michael (Commuter)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>\"We drive from Brentwood to visit family in Columbia. The drive-thru is our coffee break now. Fresh pastries for the kids, real coffee for adults. Makes the drive better.\"</p>
          <p><strong>- The Henderson Family (Brentwood)</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <h2>Questions from Brentwood Visitors</h2>
      <div class="faq-items">
        <details class="faq-item" open>
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>How far is the drive from Brentwood?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>40 minutes from Brentwood heading south on I-65. Straight shot. If you're heading to Columbia, Franklin, or anywhere south, we're basically on your way.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I order from Brentwood?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes. Use Clover to order from home or work in Brentwood. Tell us when you'll arrive and we'll have everything ready. You won't wait.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Is 40 minutes worth it for coffee?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>If you're heading south anyway, absolutely. If you're making a special trip just for coffee? Probably not. But if you're passing through on I-65, it's a great pit stop.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What's the best time to stop from Brentwood?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Early morning (5-7am) if you're leaving Brentwood early. Mid-day (2-4pm) for an afternoon coffee break. Avoid our peak times (7-8:30am, 12-1pm local time) if you want instant service.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Do I need directions?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>I-65 South from Brentwood → Dickson Exit → TN-100 South → Centerville. Or GPS: 1171 TN-100, Centerville, TN 37033. Can't miss it.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What's your payment situation?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Cash or card at the window. If you order on Clover, you pay online. Super simple.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can we bring kids?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Absolutely. You stay in the car, kids stay buckled, everyone's happy. That's the whole point of the drive-thru. No hassle with kids.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Is there seating?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Drive-thru only. No seating inside. Take your coffee in the car, at work, or at your destination. That's the design.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why-stop-section">
      <h2>Why Stop When Leaving Brentwood</h2>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Real Coffee</h3>
          <p>Not gas station coffee. Not chain coffee. Espresso pulled fresh, just for you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>You're Heading South Anyway</h3>
          <p>40 minutes from Brentwood to Centerville. If you're going to Columbia or beyond, we're on your route.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>No Getting Out</h3>
          <p>Kids stay in car. You stay comfortable. Order ahead, grab it, drive on.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Fresh Pastries & Breakfast</h3>
          <p>House-made daily. Croissants, muffins, cinnamon rolls, sandwiches. Not stale.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="menu-highlight">
      <h2>What's Available</h2>
      <div class="highlight-grid">
        <div class="highlight-block">
          <h3>Coffee Drinks</h3>
          <p>Espresso, cappuccino, latte, americano, cold brew, iced drinks. $2-6 each.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-block">
          <h3>Breakfast</h3>
          <p>Fresh pastries, breakfast sandwiches, croissants, muffins. $3-8.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-block">
          <h3>Lunch</h3>
          <p>Paninis, wraps, sandwiches, light items. $6-11.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>Next Time You Leave Brentwood</h2>
      <p>Heading south on I-65? Order on Clover before you leave. We'll have your fresh coffee and pastries ready at our drive-thru window.</p>
      <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-drivethru-centerville" class="cta-button">Order Now on Clover</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .content-block {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .content-block a {
    color: #8b4513;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .content-block a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .testimonial-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .testimonial-card p:first-child {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .testimonial-card p:last-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .why-item {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .why-item h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .why-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .highlight-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .highlight-block {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .highlight-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .highlight-block p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .faq-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: var(--light-gray);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    user-select: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-question:hover {
    background: #efefef;
  }

  .toggle-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .toggle-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #8b4513;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #6b3410;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .testimonial-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .highlight-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
